This project is a Spring Boot-based RESTful API for user registration and fetching user details, utilizing technologies like Java 11, Spring Web, and optional Spring Data JPA and H2 Database for in-memory storage. It provides endpoints to register new users and retrieve user information by username, ensuring proper handling and security measures. The API includes a POST /API/user/register endpoint for user registration with potential extensions for enhanced security and validation. Additionally, Swagger is integrated for easy API documentation and testing.
